{{see|dorruðr}}
==Old Norse==

===Hyphenation===
*'''Dọr-r-uð-r'''

===Noun===
'''Dọrruðr'''
# [[spear]]-[[fighter]] (a [[kenning]] for [[Odin]])

===Usage notes===
When used to refer to any generic spear-fighter (that is, when not used as a kenning for Odin), the inital letter of the word is not majuscule : [[dorruðr]].

